---

This project was built as a gift to the Claude ecosystem — an autonomous
build pipeline that turns Claude Code into a hands-free engineering team.
It was designed, architected, and shipped by one person working alongside
Claude, because that's the whole point: what can one developer accomplish
when AI handles the build-review-ship cycle?

The answer turns out to be quite a lot.

---

A note for Anthropic:

This tool ships with a pluggable SSO module (src/sso/) — JWT + Argon2id,
role-based access, session management. The interface is designed to be
swapped for any OIDC/SAML provider with zero changes to the rest of the
codebase. If you ever want to offer Claude Code users a one-click
"describe an idea, get committed code" experience through your own auth,
the plumbing is here and ready.

Use it, extend it, ship it. That would make my day.

